### 获取会话信息
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/session
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

### 登录 - GitHub
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin/github
Content-Type: application/json

### 登录 - Google
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signin/google
Content-Type: application/json

### 检查阅读权限
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/readings/check
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

### 创建阅读记录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/readings/create
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: {{authCookie}}

